# Horror Facts — Every Scream Has a Source

[Go]
[PostgreSQL]
[Docker]

A dark atmospheric web application that reveals the **true stories behind famous horror films**. Built with Go, PostgreSQL, and pure HTML/CSS templates.

---

## Features

- **65+ horror movies** — Russian and foreign, each with real-life facts
- **AI-powered search** — powered by DeepSeek via OpenRouter. If a movie is not in the database, AI generates the answer in the same format
- **Interactive horror map** — real-world locations that inspired famous films
- **User authentication** — registration, login, JWT tokens, cookie-based sessions
- **Dark atmospheric UI** — custom glassmorphism design with noise texture and vignette
- **Clean architecture** — Go templates, repository pattern, middleware

